remarks.format: ## Remarks 當您新增或移除項目，建立一份原始的清單，以套用變更。When you add or remove items from an , a copy of the original list is created, with the changes applied. 清單的累加變更共用記憶體盡量與較早版本的清單，並啟用以清除不再參考的任何唯一的清單資料記憶體回收。Incremental changes to a list share as much memory as possible with earlier versions of a list and enable garbage collection to clean up any unique list data that is no longer being referenced. 如需建立資訊`IImmutableList`實作中，請參閱。For information on creating an `IImmutableList` implementation, see .
